print("📡 Radar with 300 stud range and proper forward orientation")
print("🎯 Smart threat system prioritizes immediate threats over elevation")
print("⚡ Target locking prevents unwanted switching to high ground targets")
print("💥 Enhanced combat awareness with damage tracking")
print("🔊 Premium sound effects and visual feedback")
